==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chlamydomonas
<hw>Chlamydomonas</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>The type genus of the
<fam>Chlamydomonadaceae</fam>; they are solitary biflagellated plantlike
algae common in fresh water and damp soil. They multiply freely and are
often a pest around filtration plants.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Chlamydomonas</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chlamydosaurus</ent>⟦br⟧
